{"tid":102662,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過發夢中夢","createTime":"2017-01-31T18:55:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-31T19:12:45.000Z","uid":80162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2dd77274c00ec9d91677d7a5a528fab5a06f8d63","tid":102662,"uid":80162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T18:55:45.000Z","msg":"成日發夢發發下知道左自己係個夢入面<br />\n但係想醒又醒唔到 郁又郁唔到 出盡力都冇用 唯一辨法係慢慢等等到自然夢醒<br />\n有時仲要聽住現實啲風扇聲或者電視聲(有時老豆夜媽媽仲睇緊電視)<br />\n開頭仲以為比鬼壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n直到有次我係夢入面好清醒 專心聽下身邊有咩聲記住佢 夢醒之後發現跟本冇個啲聲 所以應該係夢黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n結論我發夢夢見自己夢醒但郁唔到 有冇人都試過咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ed1e04324c39159a82106871138ade1dda17023","tid":102662,"uid":503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T18:58:46.000Z","msg":"試過發夢夢見自己上中文堂訓教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n夢入邊訓訓下比FD叫醒 之後繼續上堂<br />\n屌 一醒 原來係小息 自己恰著咗 仲要跟住個堂係中文<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d7d56e3cfbff90847fbb165ec62f0eccdfab050","tid":102662,"uid":79754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T19:00:34.000Z","msg":"靈魂出竅？<br />\n出竅時要識睇手<br />\n<br />\n利申: 未試過"},{"pid":"8e786968ce22a1dca4f23511b3b051a63fffe1f8","tid":102662,"uid":80162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T19:01:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>靈魂出竅？<br />\n出竅時要識睇手<br />\n<br />\n利申: 未試過</blockquote><br />\n睇手? <br />\n我都唔知 但我細細個就發過呢啲夢 呢排又成日發番"},{"pid":"03d759a3ba1fd0b8f5f46c71713c4c69c2ae8ede","tid":102662,"uid":503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-31T19:03:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>靈魂出竅？<br />\n出竅時要識睇手<br />\n<br />\n利申: 未試過</blockquote><br />\n睇手? <br />\n我都唔知 但我細細個就發過呢啲夢 呢排又成日發番</blockquote><br />\n乜野係睇手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},